{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"75b39a6a8a","title":"万里在铁道部的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0e667793be","index":0,"year":1975,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"75b39a6a8a","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"万里","id":"1013951892","type":"人物"},{"name":"工商交通和财政","id":"1ffce755c0","type":"主题"},{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"2d92b0ddbb","name":"万里"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4335a0038f","type":"title","text":"万里在铁道部的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75b39a6a8a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d539e99010","type":"paragraph","text":"〖万里：铁道部长〗","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75b39a6a8a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1a1da80753","type":"paragraph","text":"“由于林彪修正主义路线的干扰和破坏，思想搞乱了，组织搞乱了，阶级队伍搞乱了，企业管理也搞乱了。”","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75b39a6a8a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f55ab2f98","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党领导的事业比过去低了百分之几，低了一倍，很差劲，不象话。这一点不就表现了今不如昔吗？”","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75b39a6a8a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6e4998a11","type":"paragraph","text":"“明年是第五个五年计划的第一年，还达不到过去二十几年曾经创造过的最高水平，就太丢人了。”","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75b39a6a8a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"731addf21e","type":"paragraph","text":"“生产搞不上去，搞什么共产主义？限制什么资产阶级法权？”","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75b39a6a8a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a7013c249f","type":"paragraph","text":"“我们党委书记不抓技术教育，不抓技术培训，这个党委书记就不合格。现代化的企业，党委书记不敢抓技术教育，还算什么正确路线？……政治干部不懂业务不能做干部。”","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75b39a6a8a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"807f8a3788","type":"paragraph","text":"“吉林局，《红旗》杂志上登了他们的文章，我在核心小组里讲：你看基层比我学得好。我派人下去看了，不是那么回事，是假的。你那个班子乱糟糟的，是吹牛。……大家做点实际工作，不要吹牛，要老老实实，写到做到。今后登报纸，我派人下去核实。”","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75b39a6a8a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ac3af52389","type":"paragraph","text":"“你看病为什么专门去找高级医生看病，不去请赤脚医生？我万里就是找名医到家里来看的。”","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"75b39a6a8a","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}